metadata.name: "I dressed up for you..."
metadata.description:
Her name is nana.
She is my original character.

This is a work about one of her holidays.

There are two teacups prepared for her.
She opens a women's magazine, trying her best to look pretty.
A lot of entertaining desserts are prepared.
She cries as she takes a bite of each one.

I would be happy if you look at the illustration while feeling such a story.
